snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard arrive at the High Court
snippet.description:
I can't do this anymore and want a divorce': Johnny Depp's assistant reveals the moment actor divorced Amber Heard for 'defecating on their bed' while she 'would not stop yelling' in dramatic conference call showdown over origin of faeces 

Johnny Depp's ex-fiancee Winona Ryder is set to appear at the High Court in London today in support of the actor's sensational libel claim against a newspaper over an article that labelled him a 'wife beater'.
